Adds variants of the stock highways with specific speeds (KM/H):
[list]
    [*] 2-lane, 2-way highway @ 90, 100, 110 KM/H (80 provided by stock highway)
    [*] 2-lane, 1-way highway @ 90, 100, 110, 120, 130, 140 KM/H (80 provided by stock highway)
    [*] 3-lane, 1-way highway @ 80, 90, 110, 120 KM/H (100 provided by stock highway)
    [*] 1-lane, 1-way highway/ramp @ 80 KM/H
[/list]

REQUIRES the [url=https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=1938493177]American Roads mod[/url] by Doge.

Recommended to use this with my [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1960510201]Faster Car Speeds mod[/url]

[u]Other Versions[/u]
[list]
    [*] [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1963115401]Regular KM/H[/url]
    [*] [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1960510428]Regular MPH[/url]
    [*] [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1973744473]American Roads KM/H[/url]
    [*] [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1960510592]American Roads MPH[/url]
[/list]

Want (basically) unlimited speed? Try my [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2801907991]High Speed Highway mod[/url] ([url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2801908128]American Roads ver[/url]).

Source on [url=https://github.com/ThePotatoGuy/transf2-realistic-highway-speeds]Github[/url]


