Adds variants of the stock highways with specific speeds (MPH):
[list]
    [*] 2-lane, 2-way highway @ 55, 60, 65, 70 MPH
    [*] 2-lane, 1-way highway @ 55, 60, 65, 70, 75, 80, 85 MPH
    [*] 3-lane, 1-way highway @ 55, 60, 65, 70, 75 MPH
    [*] 1-lane, 1-way highway/ramp @ 55 MPH
[/list]

REQUIRES the [url=https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=1938493177]American Roads mod[/url] by Doge.

Recommended to use this with my [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1960510201]Faster Car Speeds mod[/url]

